        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have any question, do not hesitate to write us a mail at <a href="mailto:orga.wc2017@gmail.com">orga.wc2017@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
